1 A RESOLUTION
2 To commend the Ferriday High School boys basketball team on winning the Louisiana High
3 School Athletic Association 2026 Division IV Non-Select state championship.
4 WHEREAS, it is most fitting to recognize the Ferriday High School boys basketball
5 team for their outstanding season and to commend the team on winning the Louisiana High
6 School Athletic Association 2026 Division IV Non-Select state championship; and
7 WHEREAS, the Ferriday High School Trojans captured the 2026 Division IV Non-
8 Select state title by defeating East Iberville High School, 59-55, in the championship game
9 held at Burton Coliseum in Lake Charles; and
10 WHEREAS, Marcque "BeBe" Terrell was named the MVP of the championship
11 game after scoring a game-high eighteen points, grabbing a team-high ten rebounds,
12 blocking one shot, and dishing out an assist; Caleb Washington facilitated the team's offense
13 and finished with fourteen points, nine assists, four rebounds, and three steals; and
14 WHEREAS, Robert Taylor contributed nine points, four rebounds, and two assists;
15 Demarcus Mitchell finished with seven points, two rebounds, two blocks, and four steals,
16 and Shavaris Watson added seven points, four rebounds, two steals, two assists, and one
17 block; and
18 WHEREAS, Head Coach Shawn Davis led the team to a District 2-2A title and an
19 undefeated record in district play, and the talented Trojans squad earned the top-seeded
